CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 4, 1956, page A11, reads: "A Warm Welcome... is extended Mrs. Hattie Harris Young (left) by Mrs. Ailene [Aileen] Eckstein Sawyer, wife of the president of the Frogs. Mrs. Young formerly of Atlanta, Ga. has come to make her home with her daughter and son-in-law, Atty. and Mrs. Wendell Freeland, in Pittsburgh. - Teenie Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Hattie Harris Young and Aileen Eckstein Sawyer posed in front of window with venetian blind
